{"履修期": "春学期", "主な教授言語": "フランス語", "授業目的": "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">本授業の目的は、受講者が初中級程度の内容のフランス語を聞き、話す応用力を身につけることである。</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<style>@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"MS Gothic\";\n\tpanose-1:2 11 6 9 7 2 5 8 2 4;\n\tmso-font-alt:\"ＭＳ ゴシック\";\n\tmso-font-charset:128;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:modern;\n\tmso-font-pitch:fixed;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1791491579 134217746 0 131231 0;}@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"Cambria Math\";\n\tpanose-1:2 4 5 3 5 4 6 3 2 4;\n\tmso-font-charset:0;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:roman;\n\tmso-font-pitch:variable;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1107305727 0 0 415 0;}@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"\\@MS Gothic\";\n\tpanose-1:2 11 6 9 7 2 5 8 2 4;\n\tmso-font-charset:128;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:modern;\n\tmso-font-pitch:fixed;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1791491579 134217746 0 131231 0;}p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n\t{mso-style-unhide:no;\n\tmso-style-qformat:yes;\n\tmso-style-parent:\"\";\n\tmargin:0cm;\n\tmso-pagination:widow-orphan;\n\tfont-size:12.0pt;\n\tfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\n\tmso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";}.MsoChpDefault\n\t{mso-style-type:export-only;\n\tmso-default-props:yes;\n\tfont-family:\"Cambria\",serif;\n\tmso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;\n\tmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\n\tmso-fareast-font-family:\"MS Mincho\";\n\tmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\n\tmso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;\n\tmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\n\tmso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\n\tmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\n\tmso-ansi-language:FR;\n\tmso-fareast-language:EN-US;}div.WordSection1\n\t{page:WordSection1;}</style>", "到達目標": "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">本授業では、受講者が、フランス語のやや複雑な会話やニュースや講演の概要を聞き取り、それについて話すことができるようになることを到達目標とする。</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<style>@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"MS Gothic\";\n\tpanose-1:2 11 6 9 7 2 5 8 2 4;\n\tmso-font-alt:\"ＭＳ ゴシック\";\n\tmso-font-charset:128;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:modern;\n\tmso-font-pitch:fixed;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1791491579 134217746 0 131231 0;}@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"Cambria Math\";\n\tpanose-1:2 4 5 3 5 4 6 3 2 4;\n\tmso-font-charset:0;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:roman;\n\tmso-font-pitch:variable;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1107305727 0 0 415 0;}@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"\\@MS Gothic\";\n\tpanose-1:2 11 6 9 7 2 5 8 2 4;\n\tmso-font-charset:128;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:modern;\n\tmso-font-pitch:fixed;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1791491579 134217746 0 131231 0;}p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n\t{mso-style-unhide:no;\n\tmso-style-qformat:yes;\n\tmso-style-parent:\"\";\n\tmargin:0cm;\n\tmso-pagination:widow-orphan;\n\tfont-size:12.0pt;\n\tfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\n\tmso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";}.MsoChpDefault\n\t{mso-style-type:export-only;\n\tmso-default-props:yes;\n\tfont-family:\"Cambria\",serif;\n\tmso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;\n\tmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\n\tmso-fareast-font-family:\"MS Mincho\";\n\tmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\n\tmso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;\n\tmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\n\tmso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\n\tmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\n\tmso-ansi-language:FR;\n\tmso-fareast-language:EN-US;}div.WordSection1\n\t{page:WordSection1;}</style>", "特記事項": "", "関連科目": "", "授業の概要・背景": "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n「聞く・話す・読む・書く」のすべての面にわたる総合的なフランス語学習の中で、特に 「聞く・話す」能力を向上させる。 商店でのやり取りや依頼・抗議の表現を中心に、より細かなニュアンスを聞いて理解する・ 伝える。<style>@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"MS Mincho\";\n\tpanose-1:2 2 6 9 4 2 5 8 3 4;\n\tmso-font-alt:\"ＭＳ 明朝\";\n\tmso-font-charset:128;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:modern;\n\tmso-font-pitch:fixed;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1791491579 134217746 0 131231 0;}@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"Cambria Math\";\n\tpanose-1:2 4 5 3 5 4 6 3 2 4;\n\tmso-font-charset:0;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:roman;\n\tmso-font-pitch:variable;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1107305727 0 0 415 0;}@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"\\@MS Mincho\";\n\tpanose-1:2 2 6 9 4 2 5 8 3 4;\n\tmso-font-charset:128;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:modern;\n\tmso-font-pitch:fixed;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1791491579 134217746 0 131231 0;}p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n\t{mso-style-unhide:no;\n\tmso-style-qformat:yes;\n\tmso-style-parent:\"\";\n\tmargin:0cm;\n\tmso-pagination:widow-orphan;\n\tfont-size:12.0pt;\n\tfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\n\tmso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";}.MsoChpDefault\n\t{mso-style-type:export-only;\n\tmso-default-props:yes;\n\tfont-family:\"Cambria\",serif;\n\tmso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;\n\tmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\n\tmso-fareast-font-family:\"MS Mincho\";\n\tmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\n\tmso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;\n\tmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\n\tmso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\n\tmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\n\tmso-ansi-language:FR;\n\tmso-fareast-language:EN-US;}div.WordSection1\n\t{page:WordSection1;}</style>", "授業方法": "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">授業方法は: 1.映像資料やテレビのニュースをもとに聞き取りを行う。 2.さまざまなアクティビティを通して、出題する資料に対する理解を徐々に深めていきま す。 そして、そのテーマについて所感を述べ、意見を交換します</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<style>@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"MS Mincho\";\n\tpanose-1:2 2 6 9 4 2 5 8 3 4;\n\tmso-font-alt:\"ＭＳ 明朝\";\n\tmso-font-charset:128;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:modern;\n\tmso-font-pitch:fixed;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1791491579 134217746 0 131231 0;}@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"Cambria Math\";\n\tpanose-1:2 4 5 3 5 4 6 3 2 4;\n\tmso-font-charset:0;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:roman;\n\tmso-font-pitch:variable;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1107305727 0 0 415 0;}@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"\\@MS Mincho\";\n\tpanose-1:2 2 6 9 4 2 5 8 3 4;\n\tmso-font-charset:128;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:modern;\n\tmso-font-pitch:fixed;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1791491579 134217746 0 131231 0;}p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n\t{mso-style-unhide:no;\n\tmso-style-qformat:yes;\n\tmso-style-parent:\"\";\n\tmargin:0cm;\n\tmso-pagination:widow-orphan;\n\tfont-size:12.0pt;\n\tfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\n\tmso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";}.MsoChpDefault\n\t{mso-style-type:export-only;\n\tmso-default-props:yes;\n\tfont-family:\"Cambria\",serif;\n\tmso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;\n\tmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\n\tmso-fareast-font-family:\"MS Mincho\";\n\tmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\n\tmso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;\n\tmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\n\tmso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\n\tmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\n\tmso-ansi-language:FR;\n\tmso-fareast-language:EN-US;}div.WordSection1\n\t{page:WordSection1;}</style>", "トピック": {"授業計画1": "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"JA\" ms=\"ms\" mincho\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"ms=\"mincho';mso-bidi-font-family:'ms\" mincho\";\"=\"mincho';'\" style=\"font-family:;\">フランス人が関心を持つ論題や経験した事柄について、彼らの視点を理解し</span>(<span lang=\"JA\" ms=\"ms\" mincho\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"ms=\"mincho';mso-bidi-font-family:'ms\" mincho\";\"=\"mincho';'\" style=\"font-family:;\">オーディオやビ</span><span lang=\"JA\"> </span><span lang=\"JA\" ms=\"ms\" mincho\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"ms=\"mincho';mso-bidi-font-family:'ms\" mincho\";\"=\"mincho';'\" style=\"font-family:;\">デオコンテンツの聴解</span>)<span lang=\"JA\" ms=\"ms\" mincho\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"ms=\"mincho';mso-bidi-font-family:'ms\" mincho\";\"=\"mincho';'\" style=\"font-family:;\">、</span><span lang=\"JA\"> </span><span lang=\"JA\" ms=\"ms\" mincho\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"ms=\"mincho';mso-bidi-font-family:'ms\" mincho\";\"=\"mincho';'\" style=\"font-family:;\">自分の見解を口頭で論じる術を学びます。</span><span lang=\"JA\"> </span><span lang=\"JA\" ms=\"ms\" mincho\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"ms=\"mincho';mso-bidi-font-family:'ms\" mincho\";\"=\"mincho';'\" style=\"font-family:;\">クラスで議論されるテーマは、主にフランス語圏または国際的な時事に関するものです。メディ</span><span lang=\"JA\"> </span><span lang=\"JA\" ms=\"ms\" mincho\";mso-bidi-font-family:\"ms=\"mincho';mso-bidi-font-family:'ms\" mincho\";\"=\"mincho';'\" style=\"font-family:;\">ア分析を通じてフランスと日本の文化の違いを熟考する必要があります。</span></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<style>@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"MS Mincho\";\n\tpanose-1:2 2 6 9 4 2 5 8 3 4;\n\tmso-font-alt:\"ＭＳ 明朝\";\n\tmso-font-charset:128;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:modern;\n\tmso-font-pitch:fixed;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1791491579 134217746 0 131231 0;}@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"Cambria Math\";\n\tpanose-1:2 4 5 3 5 4 6 3 2 4;\n\tmso-font-charset:0;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:roman;\n\tmso-font-pitch:variable;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1107305727 0 0 415 0;}@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"\\@MS Mincho\";\n\tpanose-1:2 2 6 9 4 2 5 8 3 4;\n\tmso-font-charset:128;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:modern;\n\tmso-font-pitch:fixed;\n\tmso-font-signature:-536870145 1791491579 134217746 0 131231 0;}p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n\t{mso-style-unhide:no;\n\tmso-style-qformat:yes;\n\tmso-style-parent:\"\";\n\tmargin:0cm;\n\tmso-pagination:widow-orphan;\n\tfont-size:12.0pt;\n\tfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\n\tmso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";}.MsoChpDefault\n\t{mso-style-type:export-only;\n\tmso-default-props:yes;\n\tfont-family:\"Cambria\",serif;\n\tmso-ascii-font-family:Cambria;\n\tmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\n\tmso-fareast-font-family:\"MS Mincho\";\n\tmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\n\tmso-hansi-font-family:Cambria;\n\tmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\n\tmso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\n\tmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\n\tmso-ansi-language:FR;\n\tmso-fareast-language:EN-US;}div.WordSection1\n\t{page:WordSection1;}</style>", "授業外学習2": "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">口頭練習は語学の上達にとって重要ですので、授業には積極的に参加してください。同時に自 己学習も重要です。復習はもちろんのこと、授業取り上げるテーマに関する文献、語彙などは 自主的に学習してください。</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<style>@font-face\n\t{font-family:\"MS Mincho\";\n\tpanose-1:2 2 6 9 4 2 5 8 3 4;\n\tmso-font-alt:\"ＭＳ 明朝\";\n\tmso-font-charset:128;\n\tmso-generic-font-family:modern;\n\tmso-font-pitch:fixed;\n\tms